Package xyz.rk0cc.willpub.pubspec.data.dependencies

Class DependenciesReferenceSet

java.lang.Object
xyz.rk0cc.willpub.pubspec.data.dependencies.DependenciesReferenceSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<DependencyReference>, Collection<DependencyReference>, Set<DependencyReference>
Direct Known Subclasses:
ImportedReferenceSet, OverrideReferenceSet
public abstract sealed class DependenciesReferenceSet extends Object implements Set<DependencyReference>, Serializable, Cloneable permits ImportedReferenceSet, OverrideReferenceSet
Contains multiple DependencyReference as a Set.
It embedded LinkedHashMap to allows more convenience way to get DependencyReference which Set can not.
Since:
1.0.0
